name: Geo Deco Ring
description:
Our signature Geo Deco pendant in an amazing statement-making ring! Gorgeous art-deco, sacred geometry inspired shape hand-cast in yellow brass. Open back making this ring adjustable to fit fingers size 5-8. Comes to a point about 1 inch above finger.

All Dea Dia items are designed and handcrafted in our Brooklyn, NY Studio.

name: Crescent Breastplate
description:
15 raw brass crescents are secured to each other in an inverted triangle pattern and attached to a double gunmetal chain with lobster claw closure. This stunning statement necklace will make you feel like a goddess any time you put it on! Perfect for holiday parties or if you want to instantly add glamour to that little black dress. The crescent moon symbolizes new beginnings and the making of dreams into reality. Because of this cyclic nature the moon it is also connected to rebirth and how our true essence really is immortal.

Chain measures 18" long
Breastplate measures 7.5" wide by 6" tall

name: Geo Deco Earrings

name: Athena Collar
description: An incredibly stunning statement necklace - not for the faint of heart! Textured brass collar has been given a beautiful patina by me. This necklace is a must for fiercely independent ladies!
